+| `plugins.allow` | Includes `clawtalk`, `whatsapp`, `restaurant-cli` | Ensures managed plugins are permitted after reconciler/observe-recovery drift |
+| `plugins.load.paths` | Includes restaurant-cli npm path | Loads the restaurant reservation plugin from the workspace npm install |
+| `plugins.entries.restaurant-cli` | Enabled with object config | Enables restaurant reservation tools while leaving provider secrets external |
 | `agents.defaults.bootstrapMaxChars` | `20000` | Prevents AGENTS.md truncation at the default 8000-char limit |
*** End Patch

